document.title: Visual and Performing Arts Content Standards for California Public Schools, Prekindergarten Through Grade Twelve

FE7351A0DFE301319B7668A86D17958E.description: Investigate and report on the essential features of modern or emerging technologies that affect or will affect visual artists and the definition of the visual arts.
